Power Finance of India Plans to Create Alternative Energy Subsidiary

-- B y   A n u r a g   J o s h i
-- 
2011-02-23T07:48:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-23/power-finance-of-india-plans-to-create-alternative-energy-subsidiary.html
Power Finance Corp., the state-owned
lender to Indian utilities, plans to create a new alternative
energy subsidiary, Chairman and Managing Director Sastnam Singh
told reporters in Mumbai today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
